  <text>Fine wires have various uses, the main ones being in the creation of <style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:misc/coil" underlined="true">Voltage Coils</style>, <style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:circuits/smd" underlined="true">SMD Components</style> and <style color="0xbbffaa">Circuits</style>.</text>
  <h3>Crafting</h3>
  <text>Fine wire can be crafted manually by cutting up foil or in a wiremill, either from <style color="0xbbffaa">1x Wire</style> if the material has that or from an <style color="0xbbffaa">Ingot</style> if it doesn't.</text>
